name: Asian Merchant Groceries & Gourmet Foods
overview: The Asian Merchant has everything you need when it comes to Asian food items and other related products. We have Japanese, Chinese, Thai, Filipino, Indian, Mongolian, Turkish, Russian and other ethnic cuisines from all over the continent. From cooking supplies and ingredients to exotic appetizers and spices, our unmatched selection of gourmet and grocery items will definitely satisfy your taste for Asian delicacies. Owner, Kimberly Tang, grew up in a household who loves to cook. As a young girl, she spent her childhood days learning family recipes from her mother who used to head the kitchen at a local Chinese restaurant. Aside from Chinese and Oriental cuisines, Kimberly also enjoys cooking other Asian delicacies which she has come to love throughout her years of experience working inside the kitchen. She prepares every meal with her own personal style, giving them a modern twist but at the same time retaining the taste and essence of genuine Asian cooking.
